WEBVTT

00:01.024 --> 00:02.397
<i>Previously on</i> The Vampire Diaries...

00:02.421 --> 00:03.456
Damon: You left your son.

00:03.505 --> 00:06.075
- You abandoned your family.
- I was ashamed!

00:06.100 --> 00:07.397
I had to get out.

00:07.483 --> 00:09.038
Sybil: It's beautiful.

00:10.044 --> 00:11.577
Elena: <i>My necklace</i>.

00:11.772 --> 00:14.615
I thought I'd never see it
again. Thank you.

00:14.725 --> 00:17.219
♪♪

00:17.294 --> 00:20.294
You want your freedom
in exchange for these two girls.

00:20.418 --> 00:22.419
Stefan: I'll do it.
Just let the girls go.

00:22.481 --> 00:24.364
I could become
the ripper that you want.

00:24.450 --> 00:26.825
- You'd turn your humanity off?
- For a short time, yes.

00:26.863 --> 00:29.997
I predict that, after a year with
me, you won't want to leave.

00:30.077 --> 00:32.028
When it's over, you let me
and my brother go.

00:32.091 --> 00:35.473
I made a deal. I serve him
for a year and then I'm done.

00:35.542 --> 00:37.255
Caroline:
<i>What are you going to do?</i>

00:37.320 --> 00:39.044
You're gonna want
to get under the hood

00:39.110 --> 00:41.345
and flip that humanity switch,
Stefan.

00:41.497 --> 00:43.913
Won't be so painful.

